title: R Ladies Thessaloniki First Meetup [Introduction to R]
description:
This event is organized by R Ladies Thessaloniki which is the local chapter of R Ladies Global for the city of Thessaloniki.

R Ladies is an organization that promotes gender diversity in the R community worldwide.

In this first meetup we will introduce the R Ladies organization and its mission. Additionally, we will also provide a taste of the R programming language in the context of data analysis.

The event will finalize with a Q&A session which will provide both the attendees and the organizers with a clear view of what events to organize in the future.

Language: English
